{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/ar/media-center/qatar-foundations-edi-hosts-istemed-camp-2019","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"aa985270-02d0-579a-bb33-6439c60c5b6e","slug":"qatar-foundations-edi-hosts-istemed-camp-2019","title":"معهد التطوير التربوي يستضيف مخيم \"iSTEMed\" لعام 2019","date":"2019-03-24","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"6osgodAE6cIuiqSAOQugAs"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"0fb5ddeb-7a13-55d4-a2fd-26c2668f5761","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>أقام معهد التطوير التربوي، وهو جزء من التعليم ما قبل الجامعي في مؤسسة قطر، مخيم \" iSTEMed \" للعام 2019، في أكاديمية العوسج في الفترة من 21 وحتى 23 مارس، تحت شعار \"تفعيل STEM\"، وبرعاية شركة إكسون موبيل.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"bf782269-441b-5f4b-ba80-a7def050f475","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"d1bd7efc-ebd4-5a91-80f5-70a4b6265873","title":"Image2","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":1508,"height":1006}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=560&h=300&q=85 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85 1120w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=1508&h=808&q=85 1508w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed5373975ac5858a96d3e12ab/Image2.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85&fm=webp","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/8A4e26m9v1eDVdh02jaLa/346a9a8ed537397